headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Business Class
content: Do you have a taste for the brutally fast, the brutally efficient or the just plain brutal?  Whatever your preference, the latest wave of transport options in retailers across Los Santos is bound to hit your sweet spot. From the monstrous HVY Brickade at Warstock Cache and Carry to the superfast Buckingham Nimbus at Elitas Travel, getting from A to B has never looked and felt this good.
